description:
Application for minor amendment to planning permission ref: P081325 dated 12 December 2008 for:
a)	changes to the roof including: and increase in roof area, relocated solar water heating panels, introduction of plant and passive smoke shafts; 
b)	increase in height of the front of the building and introduction of a parapet to the rear of the building;
c)	at basement level an increase in floor area (260sqm),  commercial cycle storage moved to the basement, addition of a habitable room (bedroom) to the residential basement area;
d)	introduction of pavement lights (lighting basement);
e)	at ground floor level the amalgamation of the two show rooms approved into one unit, relocation of the commercial refuse storage and relocation of bike storage (x10) to the basement; commercial entrance changed and introduction of fire escape route and door to front street elevation;
f)	at all levels: increase in size (floor area) at all levels, increase in the number of windows, repositioning of the commercial core (lift and main stair location) addition of riser shafts, introduction of an external fire escape stair to the rear, introduction of toilets and other ancillary facilities;
g)	within the residential part of the development, alteration of the internal reconfigurations including layout of rooms, stair locations, and also the top unitâ€™s layout has been flipped (bedrooms above living areas);
h)	the increase in size of the residential units at fifth and sixth floors;
i)	changes to the front elevation including a reduction of floor to ceiling heights at all levels, in particular at ground floor level, alteration to the treatment around the Courtyard garage, changes to the entrance to the building and refuse storage etc
